    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>In modern usage, buildings that house banks that specialize in the exchange of stocks and securities. The term historically refers to buildings in which the merchants of a town assemble for the transaction of business.</Note_Text>
